Unmodified copies of the Software MAY be shared with others for the sole
purpose of letting them read it, evaluate it, or set up their own,
separate, direct use of it (for example: forking the public repository,
linking to it, teaching from it, or mirroring it as-is). That is not the
same as shipping it to someone as part of a product or service you give
