3. WHAT THIS DOES NOT RESTRICT

To be explicit about how far Section 2 goes and no further: you may run
the Software, modified or not, inside your own organization, for your
own agents, your own internal tooling, and your own infrastructure --
including at a for-profit company -- for as long as nobody outside your
organization ends up running, receiving, or being served by that copy
as part of something you gave them.

